Amendment No. 5 to HB2631
Jones J
Signature of Sponsor
AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 2690* House Bill No. 2631
by adding the following as a new, appropriately designated section immediately preceding the
antepenultimate section and redesignating the subsequent sections accordingly:
SECTION __.
Item 1. The appropriation in Section 1, Title III-9, Item 1.5, to the Department of
Education for the Education Freedom Scholarship Program, as identified on Page B-104
of the 2026-2027 Budget Document, is reduced by the sum of $303,920,000.
Item 2. In addition to any other funds appropriated by the provisions of this act,
there is appropriated the sum of $303,920,000 to the Department of Agriculture for the
sole purpose of providing grants to small family farmers in Tennessee who are in need
of financial assistance on account of tariffs and other economic pressures.
